body:
@concretevitamin and I ran into an issue while trying to replicate setup for a project manually SSHing into separate VMs. We had some issues replicating each other's results, so we ended up just sharing the VM in the end (e.g. add other person's pubkey to VM authorized_keys). 

The following feature would be nice: Launch a cpunode, do a bunch of setup cmds, then capture into Task.setup.

One step further: can we automatically create a Dockerfile/image with this kind of feature?
